        <p>To tackle e-waste, it's crucial to promote awareness and responsible disposal practices. Encourage recycling programs and electronic take-back initiatives to properly dispose of old devices. Support policies that hold manufacturers accountable for the lifecycle of their products, including design for disassembly and recycling. Emphasize the importance of reducing electronic consumption and opting for repair and refurbishment whenever possible.</p>
    </div>
